Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us. At Neat Software Co., we are committed to respecting your privacy regarding any information we may collect through our website,
https://neat.software
, and the applications and services we own and operate.
Information We Collect
We may collect information to improve our services and provide you with the best possible experience. This includes:
Anonymous Analytics:
We may gather non-personally identifiable information about your interactions with our apps and website, such as usage patterns and device details. This data helps us understand how our products are used and identify areas for improvement.
Personal Information:
We only request personal information, such as your name or email address, when it is essential to provide a service you have requested. This information is collected with your knowledge and consent.
How We Use Your Data
Any data we collect is used solely for the purposes described below:
To enhance the functionality and performance of our apps and website.
To provide you with the services you request.
To analyze and improve the user experience through aggregated, anonymous data.
Data Retention and Protection
We retain collected information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. We protect the data we store using commercially acceptable practices to prevent loss, theft, unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, or modification.
Sharing Information
We do not share any personally identifiable information with third parties unless required by law. Anonymous analytics data may be shared with trusted service providers to help us analyze usage trends and improve our services.
Third-Party Links
Our website and apps may contain links to external sites not operated by us. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites. Please review their privacy policies before engaging with their services.
Your Choices
You are not obligated to provide personal information, but declining to do so may limit your access to certain features or services. By continuing to use our website or apps, you acknowledge and agree to the practices described in this policy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices or how we handle your data, please
contact us
.
